    <header class="col">
  <p class="eyebrow">Agents of Chaos · from the network map</p>
  <h1>The most connected company in AI is not OpenAI</h1>
  <p class="dek">We maintain a map of the agentic economy: 188 companies that build, deploy, or secure AI agents, wired together by 492 documented relationships. When you embed that graph and let the connections speak, one company sits further out on the first latent dimension than anything else on the map. It is Anthropic, and the math behind that dot tells a sharper story about the AI race than most market commentary does.</p>
</header>

